<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Mikelic in Trieste?"] </F>
  [Text] Ljubljana, Trieste -- The speculations of the 
Italian right wing with Istria and Dalmatia are limitless, the 
Trieste correspondent of Ljubljana DELO writes. He proves this 
with an invitation to visit Trieste that the neofascist party's 
councilor Sergio Giacomelli has extended to the Petrinja 
