<H3> <TI>   Uhde Welcomes Prospects for EU Agreement </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Uhde Welcomes Prospects for EU Agreement </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2106185594 Prague CTK in English 1554 GMT 21 Jun 94 -- FOR 
