<H3> <TI>   LSU, CMSS Agree To Merge by End of Sep </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    LSU, CMSS Agree To Merge by End of Sep </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2206113394 Prague CTK in English 1054 GMT 22 Jun 94 -- FOR 
