  [Text] Sofia, June 22 (BTA) -- The leader of the Bulgarian 
Socialist Party (BSP) Zhan Videnov today met with Yugoslav 
Ambassador Rados Smilkovic, the BSP Press Office reported. 
  At the meeting, which was held at the ambassador's request, 
the two shared views on bilateral cooperation on the state and 
political-party level. Smilkovic commended the BSP role in the 
Bulgarian-Yugoslav dialogue, said the Press Office. Smilkovic 
