<F P=100> BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Abdic Issues New `War Threats' in Bihac Region </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Abdic Issues New `War Threats' in Bihac Region </PHRASE></F></HT>

