<H3> <TI>   `Status Quo' on Border Reported </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Status Quo' on Border Reported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2406093694 Skopje MILS-NEWS in English 24 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU2406093694 </F>
<F P=104>  Skopje MILS-NEWS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Status Quo on Border Line"] </F>
  [Text] The situation with Serbian troops stationed on the 
Macedonian [The Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia -- FYROM] 
territory near Kriva Palanka is in a status quo. The two 
countries' soldiers are positioned only few hundred meters away 
from each other. There are no incidents and the region is 
regularly flown over by UNPROFOR [UN Protection Forces] 
helicopters. The anxiety of the local population loosens, but 
farmers are prevented from cultivating their land as it is on 
the territory presently usurped by Serbian troops. 

</TEXT>

